<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١ - وَكُلُّ أَخٍ مُفَارِقُهُ أَخُوهُ ... لِنِيَّتِهِ كَمَا انْقَطَعَ الْجَرِيرُ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٢ - وَمَا يَبْقَى عَلَى الْحَدَثَانِ شَيْءٌ ... عَلَيْهِ دَوَائِرُ الدُّنْيَا تَدُورُ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(٧٨٩)</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ امْرُؤُ الْقَيسِ:</span> <span class="c2">(الطويل)</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>١ - إِذَا قُلْتُ هذَا صَاحبٌ قَدْ رَضِيتُهُ ... وَقَرَّتْ بِهِ عَيْنِي تَبَدَّلْتُ آخَرًا<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٧٩٠)</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ آخَرُ:</span> <span class="c2">(الطويل)</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>١ - لِكُلِّ اجْتمَاعٍ مِنْ خَلِيلَيْنِ فُرْقَهٌّ ... وَكُلُّ الَّذِي دُونَ الْفِرَاقِ قَلِيلُ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>٢ - وإِنَّ افْتِقَادِي وَاحِدًا بَعدَ وَاحِدٍ ... دَلِيلٌ عَلَى أَنْ لا يَدُوُم خَلِيلُ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(٧٩١)</span><a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ يَحْيِى بنُ زِيادٍ:</span> <span class="c2">(البسيط)</span><a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>١ - وَصَاحِبَيْنِ أَذَاعَ الدَّهْرُ بَينَهمَا ... بِفُرْقَةٍ وَاللَّيَالِي تَقْطَعُ الْقَرَنَا<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>٢ - كَانَا خَلِيلَيْنِ لَمَّ تُقْرَعْ صَفَاتُهُمَا ... فَخَانَ دَهْرُهُمَا مِنْ بَعْدِ مَا أَمِنَا<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c2">(٧٩٢)</span><a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ النَّابغَةُ الْجَعْدِيُّ:</span> <span class="c2">(المتقارب)</span><a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>١ - وَذلِكَ مِنْ وَقَعَاتِ الْمَنُونِ ... فَخَلِّي إِلَيْكِ وَلا تَعْجَبِي<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>